019-05-30T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"佢好精準深刻嘅哲學ok<br />\n好好笑好重情嘅日常ok<br />\n但犬夾係中間，兩面去唔到，故仔仲要開波就估到尾，法師一定會無事，同珊瑚一齊，犬傾幾句就新招，個招式仲要畫面表達唔到，基本上同一招唔同招式叫法咁<br />\n<br />\n純粹覺得好哂，好似浦澤佢係寫偵探式嘅，換題材都唔會換方式，完全發揮到佢才能<br />\n犬我覺得係高橋最敗筆，當然名氣另計"},{"pid":"32febddd07a2319316c70439cd6d9d72bf9253a9","tid":1178482,"uid":171157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"計近十幾年<br />\n科幻漫畫代表人物係咪貳瓶勉"},{"pid":"5b81ce48e634d99b5bcd8a4c7cd21cd714d596af","tid":1178482,"uid":82749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"見到幪面超人都係科幻已經唔洗睇"},{"pid":"ea13391fd0d5e2eaf157639d2a397afcb67da908","tid":1178482,"uid":52263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b81ce48e634d99b5bcd8a4c7cd21cd714d596af","tid":1178482,"uid":82749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"見到幪面超人都係科幻已經唔洗睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"石之森一開始講改造喎<br />\n咁寄生獸又唔洗睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0866b5bdf84a4651793bb7e6b09f6c9a307d0d","tid":1178482,"uid":52263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea13391fd0d5e2eaf157639d2a397afcb67da908","tid":1178482,"uid":52263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b81ce48e634d99b5bcd8a4c7cd21cd714d596af","tid":1178482,"uid":82749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"見到幪面超人都係科幻已經唔洗睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"石之森一開始講改造喎<br />\n咁寄生獸又唔洗睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"石之森手頭小露寶, 閃電人, 電腦奇俠全部都係科幻<br />\n科普幻想/科學幻想, 究竟幪面超人有咩問題<img src=\"/asset